    <text>
        <body>
            <div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1867-07-13T23:59:59-05:00" frus:doc-dateTime-min="1867-07-13T00:00:00-05:00" n="50" subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d50">
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">Mr. <persName type="from">Seward</persName> to
                                    Mr. <persName type="to">McCook</persName>.</hi>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <seg rendition="#left">[Confidential.] <lb/> No. 33.]</seg>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Department of State</hi>,<lb/>
                            <hi rend="italic">Washington</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1867-07-13">
                            <hi rend="italic">July 13,
                                        1867</hi>
                        </date>.</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p rend="flushleft">Mr. <hi rend="smallcaps">McCook</hi>,<lb/>
                    <hi rend="italic">Honolulu:</hi>
                </p>
                <p>
                    <hi rend="smallcaps">Sir</hi>: Your private note written on the 27th
                                of June, on the eve of your departure from San Francisco for
                                Honolulu, has just been received.</p>
                <p>You have leave to come to this place at the next meeting of Congress,
                                which will probably take place in November.</p>
                <p>You are at liberty to sound the proper authority on the large subject
                                mentioned in your note and ascertain probable conditions. You may
                                confidentially receive overtures and communicate the same to me.</p>
                <p>I will act upon your suggestion in that relation in regard to a party
                                now here.</p>
                <p>I am, etc.,</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">William H.
                                Seward.</hi>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
